# signal-filter-designer

## get start

1. install Anaconda (python3.8)
2. install pycharm
3. install pyqt5 & pyqt5-tools & config tools
4. open this project with pycharm

## reference
- https://github.com/chipmuenk/pyfda

## attention!!
- The Author do not have a professional background in digital signals, so there are many imprecise aspects of this program
- so much bugs;
